<p>We do not comment on specific works or their &#8220;chances.&#8221; The way you make the ballot is to come to the attention of enough members of WSFS that they decide to nominate your work. Self-published authors have been finalists and have won the Hugo Award.</p>
<p>Kevin Standlee</p>
